Additional disaster assistance is available to the state of California to help with recovery efforts from the #LosAngelesFires. 

@POTUS authorized the cost-share for emergency protective measures to increase from 75% to 100%.

Learn more: https://t.co/6YRvyz0Oj4 https://t.co/PyPFMnmI57

